title: Be Intentional With Your Time and Your Money (Hour 2)
description:
John Delony & Rachel Cruze discuss:

Going into debt to buy out your ex,

Saving for baby or a house,

Managing a larger income,

Dealing with loneliness after divorce,


Want a plan for your money? Find out where to start: https://bit.ly/3nInETX
Listen to all The Ramsey Network podcasts: https://bit.ly/3GxiXm6
